{"word":"H6805 - צָעַד - tsâʻad - tsaw-ad' - Bring","slug":"H6805","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">צָעַד</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>tsâʻad"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>tsaw-ad'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Bring"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E6;&#x05E2;&#x05D3; - tsa&#x0302;&#x201B;ad</b> - <i>tsaw-ad'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>pace</i>, that is, <i>step</i> regularly; (upward) to <i>mount</i>; (along) to <i>march</i>; (down and causatively) to <i>hurl: - </i>bring, go, march (through), run over."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4703\">H4703</a>, <a href=\"#/H6806\">H6806</a>, <a href=\"#/H6807\">H6807</a>"}]}